Executive: Hello?
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Haan.
Customer: Hello. Sorry sir, sorry sir, sorry sir. Acha aapko lag gaya kya call. Sir Vanshika baat kar rahi hu, Vanshika baat kar rahi hu. Are to mai aapko call kar raha hu na.
Executive: Hello. Ji sir.
Customer: Are mai aap hi ko to call kar raha hu.
Customer: Sir mere paas mam ka call aaya tha na unko guide karna hai. Sir ke paas.
Executive: Are to tumne tumne jo mail kiya hai na wo mail mat kariye aap whatsapp kijiye.
Customer: Thik hai, thik hai sir. Maine isliye unse pucha hai to wo phone nahi tha. Mail possible nahi hai. Mail mail ke ha mail possible nahi hoga. Whatsapp kijiye aap.
Customer: Okay sir, koi baat nahi. Haan.
